those tricks were so easy:
1. The first trick was a special deck of cards (I think it's called the invisible deck) that has two cards stuck together by some sort of cement material in the deck. This means half the cards are flipped over. Harris new which card was opposite of the Jack of Diamonds, so he just pulled apart those two cards, getting the Jack of Diamonds to appear face down.
2. No explanation needed :)
3. I'm not completely sure about this, but there was a piece of wire hidden in the cloth, that moves when triggered by a subtle hand movement. This causes the stool to rise away when a certain amount of pressure is put on the cloth.
